# Mobile — Compose Multiplatform

## Tech Stack

- Kotlin 2.3.10 + Compose Multiplatform 1.10.1
- MVIKotlin 4.3.0 (state management)
- Koin 4.1.1 (DI)
- Ktor 3.3.3 (networking)
- moko-resources 0.26.0 (strings, colors, images)
- Compose Navigation with `@Serializable` screens
- Android: compileSdk 36, minSdk 26, targetSdk 36

## Project Structure

```
android/app/                # Android entry point
iosApp/                     # iOS entry point
shared/
├── main/                   # Aggregation, Koin init, NavHost, iOS export
├── common/                 # CoroutineDispatchers, base classes, extensions
├── common-resources/       # moko-resources (strings, colors, images)
├── common-ui/              # KmmTemplateTheme, design system, reusable components
├── core-presentation/      # BaseViewModel, MVIKotlin binding
├── core-navigation/        # Screen interface + routes
└── feature-*/              # Feature modules (api/impl/presentation/ui)
build-logic/                # Convention plugins
gradle/libs.versions.toml   # Version catalog
```

## Feature Architecture (4 modules)

Each feature is split into 4 submodules:

| Module           | Contents                                         | Depends on              |
|------------------|--------------------------------------------------|-------------------------|
| **api**          | Store interface (State, Intent, Label)           | —                       |
| **impl**         | Executor, Reducer, Repository, StoreFactory, DI  | api                     |
| **presentation** | ViewModel, mappers, UI State/Label               | api, core-presentation  |
| **ui**           | Composable screens, Screen API                   | presentation, common-ui |

Dependency graph:
```
ui → presentation → api
impl → api
```

## Naming Conventions

| Entity       | Pattern                              | Example                              |
|--------------|--------------------------------------|--------------------------------------|
| Store        | `{Feature}Store`                     | `UserListStore`                      |
| Executor     | `{Feature}Executor`                  | `UserListExecutor`                   |
| Reducer      | `{Feature}Reducer`                   | `UserListReducer`                    |
| StoreFactory | `{Feature}StoreFactory`              | `UserListStoreFactory`               |
| ViewModel    | `{Feature}ViewModel`                 | `UserListViewModel`                  |
| Repository   | `{Feature}Repository`                | `UserListRepository`                 |
| Screen       | `{Feature}Screen`                    | `UserListScreen`                     |
| UI State     | `Ui{Feature}State`                   | `UiUserListState`                    |
| UI Label     | `Ui{Feature}Label`                   | `UiUserListLabel`                    |
| DI impl      | `feature{Feature}ImplModule`         | `featureUserListImplModule`          |
| DI present.  | `feature{Feature}PresentationModule` | `featureUserListPresentationModule`  |
